node.text:
A brief guide to doing the Inktober challenge.⁣
Special thanks to @artsnacks for making the #inktober2020 art box. I seriously love these art boxes!⁣ ⁣
⁣
To order one hit the link in the @inktober profile.⁣
⁣
-Jake

node.text:
The Star Catcher⁣
⁣
Taking a break from App Bots for the next month or so as I start working on my Inktober drawings. ⁣
⁣
Just wanted to thank everyone for being into this silly idea of apps as robots. App Bots will return!⁣
⁣
#starcatcher #inktober #spacepunks #characterdesign #comiccharacter #comicartist

⁣

This has been a great design problem to solve each morning as I try to fit different cultural icons into the bot constraint I've set for myself. ⁣
⁣
#siperman #spidey #spiderbot #robot #mech #marvel #characterdesign ⁣
